description:
In this video, I’ll show you how I install a window insulation kit to seal up drafty windows and cut down on heat loss. These kits are one of the easiest DIY upgrades for improving home energy efficiency. If your windows feel cold or leaky, this is the fix.

Learn How to Winterize Your Home 👉🏼 https://youtu.be/3FG0K9LpkXU

If you found this video helpful, please subscribe. Hope you enjoy. Cheers!
title: Save Your $$$ Fix For Drafty Windows
